title: Celebrity Gossip Part 2 - Tom And Gisele Lawyer Up
description: Today’s theme is: divorce. Things have been rocky for Tom Brady and Gisele lately, but now it looks like things might be getting seriously bad. Plus, we finally have an idea about what happened on that private plane in 2016 between Brad Pitt, Angelina Jolie, and their children that led to their divorce.
